20
00:02:53.433 --> 00:03:03.113
Do not imagine the particles as tiny ice cubes or tiny wet
drops. The dots are a model. They show spacing and
movement, not microscopic photographs.

21
00:03:03.113 --> 00:03:09.212
The chemist move here is: if the state changes, ask how
the particles are arranged and moving.
